ed="T" n="0848a09"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0848a09"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000034739"><placeName>成都府</placeName><placeName>法聚寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A012854">法江</persName>傳（<persName key="A019457">興善寺異僧</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0848a10"/><persName key="A012854">釋法江</persName>者，<placeName key="PL000000009926">江東</placeName>人也，來遊<placeName key="PL000000035107">岷蜀</placeName>，居于<placeName key="PL000000034739">法聚<lb
    ed="T" n="0848a11"/>寺</placeName>──<ref type="place" target="#PL000000034739">寺</ref>即<date from-iso="+0581-03-06" key="j19333311946884" to-iso="+0618-04-15">隋</date><persName key="A005582"><persName>蜀王</persName><persName>秀</persName></persName>之造也。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000034739">寺</ref>內有<date key="j19406121942058" notAfter-iso="+0605-01-27" notBefore-iso="+0601-02-11"><name>仁壽</name>中</date><persName key="A004324">文<lb
ed="T" n="0848a12"/>帝</persName>樹舍利塔。<persName key="A012854">江</persName>以慈憫為懷，多逆知其來，<lb
ed="T" n="0848a13"/>言無少誤。甞在房中謂門人曰：「外有萬餘<lb
ed="T" n="0848a14"/>人，盡戴帽形且攣䠰<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1805"/>，從<ref type="person" target="#A012854">吾</ref>乞救。汝速出<ref type="place" target="#PL000000034739">寺</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0848a15"/>外求之。」不見人物，弟子怪<ref type="person" target="#A012854">師</ref>之言何其倒<lb
ed="T" n="0848a16"/>亂。徙倚<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1806"/>之間，有數十人荷檐竹器中螺子<lb
ed="T" n="0848a17"/>至，<persName key="A012854">江</persName>曰：「此之是歟！」命取錢贖之，投于水中<lb
ed="T" n="0848a18"/>矣。</p><p xml:id="pT50p0848a1901"><lb
ed="T" n="0848a19"/>又<placeName key="PL000000042218"><placeName>長安</placeName><placeName>大興善寺</placeName></placeName>，本<date from-iso="+0581-03-06" key="j19333311946884" to-iso="+0618-04-15"><name>隋</name></date><placeName key="PL000000042308">舍衛寺</placeName>也，至<date notBefore-iso="+0668-04-25" key="j19651571965860" notAfter-iso="+0670-03-29"><name>唐</name><name><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>先天</sic><corr>總章</corr></choice></name><lb
ed="T" n="0848a20"/>中</date>火災<ptr target="#n636"/>，殿宇蕩然，唯遺基耳――<date notBefore-iso="+0656-02-10" key="j19606991962581" notAfter-iso="+0661-04-06"><name>明慶</name>中</date><placeName key="PL000000042104">東明觀</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0848a21"/>道士<persName key="A005866">李榮</persName>者，本<placeName key="PL000000035431">巴西</placeName>人也，好事薄徒，多與<lb
ed="T" n="0848a22"/><name>釋</name>子爭競優劣<ptr target="#n637"/>――，<persName key="A005866">榮</persName>來<placeName key="PL000000057371">玄都觀</placeName>，因率黃冠指<lb
ed="T" n="0848a23"/>其灰燼而嘲之曰：「道善何曾善？言興且不<lb
ed="T" n="0848a24"/>興。如來燒赤盡，唯有一群僧。」僧中有憤其<lb
ed="T" n="0848a25"/>異宗譏誚者，急<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>慕</sic><corr>募</corr></choice>勸重新締構，復廣於前。十<lb
ed="T" n="0848a26"/>二畝之地，化緣雖日盈千萬，計未能成。僧<lb
ed="T" n="0848a27"/>眾搔首躇蹰，未知何理克成。忽有一<ref type="person" target="#A019457">僧</ref>，衣<lb
ed="T" n="0848a28"/>服麁弊，形容憔悴，負一破囊入緣，言：「速了<lb
ed="T" n="0848a29"/>佛殿。」步驟而去。啟視之，則黃金也，校耒<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1807"/>之<pb ed="T" n="0848b" xml:id="T50.2061.0848b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0848b01"/>一千兩矣。時人奇之，由此檀施<ptr type="glossary" target="#g237"/>日繁，殿速<lb
ed="T" n="0848b02"/>成矣。</p>
